# <span class="keyword">GemFire</span> Cache Transactions

Use <span class="keyword">GemFire</span> cache transactions to group the execution of cache operations and to gain the control offered by transactional commit and rollback. <span class="keyword">GemFire</span> cache transactions control operations within the <span class="keyword">GemFire</span> cache while the <span class="keyword">GemFire</span> distributed system handles data distribution in the usual way.

